{"id":11,"ayahs":[{"number":70,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟ ٱدْعُ لَنَا رَبَّكَ يُبَيِّن لَّنَا مَا هِىَ إِنَّ ٱلْبَقَرَ تَشَٰبَهَ عَلَيْنَا وَإِنَّآ إِن شَآءَ ٱللَّهُ لَمُهْتَدُونَ","translation":"Said' they: \"Pray on our behalf unto thy Sustainer that He make clear to us what she is to be like, for to us all cows resemble one another; and then, if God so wills, we shall truly be guided aright!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/77.mp3","surahId":2,"words":[{"id":59432,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"তারা বলেছিল","audioUrl":"wbw/002_070_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59433,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱدْعُ","translation":"''তুমি দোয়া করো","audioUrl":"wbw/002_070_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59434,"position":3,"arabic":"لَنَا","translation":"আমদের জন্য","audioUrl":"wbw/002_070_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59435,"position":4,"arabic":"رَبَّكَ","translation":"তোমার রবের কাছে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_070_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59436,"position":5,"arabic":"يُبَيِّن","translation":"তিনি বর্ণনা করেন (যেন)","audioUrl":"wbw/002_070_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59437,"position":6,"arabic":"لَّنَا","translation":"আমাদের জন্য","audioUrl":"wbw/002_070_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59438,"position":7,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"কেমন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_070_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59439,"position":8,"arabic":"هِىَ","translation":"তা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_070_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59440,"position":9,"arabic":"إِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/002_070_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59441,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلْبَقَرَ","translation":"গাভীটি","audioUrl":"wbw/002_070_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59442,"position":11,"arabic":"تَشَـٰبَهَ","translation":"একই রকম","audioUrl":"wbw/002_070_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59443,"position":12,"arabic":"عَلَيْنَا","translation":"আমাদের কাছে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_070_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59444,"position":13,"arabic":"وَإِنَّآ","translation":"এবং নিশ্চয়ই আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_070_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59445,"position":14,"arabic":"إِن","translation":"যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/002_070_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59446,"position":15,"arabic":"شَآءَ","translation":"চান","audioUrl":"wbw/002_070_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59447,"position":16,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ্‌","audioUrl":"wbw/002_070_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59448,"position":17,"arabic":"لَمُهْتَدُونَ","translation":"অবশ্যই সঠিক জ্ঞান প্রাপ্ত হব''","audioUrl":"wbw/002_070_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59449,"position":18,"arabic":"٧٠","translation":"(৭০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":71,"arabic":"قَالَ إِنَّهُۥ يَقُولُ إِنَّهَا بَقَرَةٌۭ لَّا ذَلُولٌۭ تُثِيرُ ٱلْأَرْضَ وَلَا تَسْقِى ٱلْحَرْثَ مُسَلَّمَةٌۭ لَّا شِيَةَ فِيهَا ۚ قَالُوا۟ ٱلْـَٰٔنَ جِئْتَ بِٱلْحَقِّ ۚ فَذَبَحُوهَا وَمَا كَادُوا۟ يَفْعَلُونَ","translation":"[Moses] answered: \"Behold, He says it is to be a cow not broken-in to plough the earth or to water the crops, free of fault, without markings of any other colour.\"Said they: \"At last thou hast brought out the truth!\"-and thereupon they sacrificed her, although they had almost left it undone.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/78.mp3","surahId":2,"words":[{"id":60342,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"(মূসা) বলল","audioUrl":"wbw/002_071_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60343,"position":2,"arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ","translation":"''তিনি নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/002_071_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60344,"position":3,"arabic":"يَقُولُ","translation":"বলেন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_071_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60345,"position":4,"arabic":"إِنَّهَا","translation":"''তা নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/002_071_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60346,"position":5,"arabic":"بَقَرَةٌۭ","translation":"একটি গাভী","audioUrl":"wbw/002_071_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60347,"position":6,"arabic":"لَّا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/002_071_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60348,"position":7,"arabic":"ذَلُولٌۭ","translation":"লাগান হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_071_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60349,"position":8,"arabic":"تُثِيرُ","translation":"চাষে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_071_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60350,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضَ","translation":"জমি","audioUrl":"wbw/002_071_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60351,"position":10,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"আর না","audioUrl":"wbw/002_071_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60352,"position":11,"arabic":"تَسْقِى","translation":"সেচ করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_071_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60353,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱلْحَرْثَ","translation":"ক্ষেতে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_071_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60354,"position":13,"arabic":"مُسَلَّمَةٌۭ","translation":"সুস্থ্য","audioUrl":"wbw/002_071_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60355,"position":14,"arabic":"لَّا","translation":"নেই","audioUrl":"wbw/002_071_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60356,"position":15,"arabic":"شِيَةَ","translation":"কোনো খুঁত","audioUrl":"wbw/002_071_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60357,"position":16,"arabic":"فِيهَا ۚ","translation":"তার মধ্যে''","audioUrl":"wbw/002_071_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60359,"position":17,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"তারা বলেছিল","audioUrl":"wbw/002_071_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60360,"position":18,"arabic":"ٱلْـَٔـٰنَ","translation":"''এখন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_071_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60361,"position":19,"arabic":"جِئْتَ","translation":"তুমি এনেছ (বর্ণনা)","audioUrl":"wbw/002_071_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60362,"position":20,"arabic":"بِٱلْحَقِّ ۚ","translation":"সঠিক তথ্য নিয়ে''","audioUrl":"wbw/002_071_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60364,"position":21,"arabic":"فَذَبَحُوهَا","translation":"তারা জবাই করল তখন তা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_071_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60365,"position":22,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/002_071_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60366,"position":23,"arabic":"كَادُوا۟","translation":"আগ্রহী ছিল","audioUrl":"wbw/002_071_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60367,"position":24,"arabic":"يَفْعَلُونَ","translation":"তারা করতে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_071_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60368,"position":25,"arabic":"٧١","translation":"(৭১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":72,"arabic":"وَإِذْ قَتَلْتُمْ نَفْسًۭا فَٱدَّٰرَْٰٔتُمْ فِيهَا ۖ وَٱللَّهُ مُخْرِجٌۭ مَّا كُنتُمْ تَكْتُمُونَ","translation":"For, O children of Israel, because you had slain a human being and then cast the blame for this [crime] upon one another -although God will bring to light what you would conceals","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/79.mp3","surahId":2,"words":[{"id":60421,"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذْ","translation":"এবং (স্মরণ করো) যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_072_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60422,"position":2,"arabic":"قَتَلْتُمْ","translation":"তোমরা হত্যা করেছিলে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_072_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60423,"position":3,"arabic":"نَفْسًۭا","translation":"এক ব্যক্তিকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_072_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60424,"position":4,"arabic":"فَٱدَّٰرَْٰٔتُمْ","translation":"তোমরা অতঃপর একে অন্যের ওপর দোষ চাপাচ্ছিলে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_072_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60425,"position":5,"arabic":"فِيهَا ۖ","translation":"সে ব্যাপারে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_072_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60427,"position":6,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","translation":"এবং আল্লাহ্‌","audioUrl":"wbw/002_072_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60428,"position":7,"arabic":"مُخْرِجٌۭ","translation":"প্রকাশকারী","audioUrl":"wbw/002_072_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60429,"position":8,"arabic":"مَّا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_072_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60430,"position":9,"arabic":"كُنتُمْ","translation":"(আপনি)","audioUrl":"wbw/002_072_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60431,"position":10,"arabic":"تَكْتُمُونَ","translation":"তোমরা গোপন করছিলে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_072_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60432,"position":11,"arabic":"٧٢","translation":"(৭২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":73,"arabic":"فَقُلْنَا ٱضْرِبُوهُ بِبَعْضِهَا ۚ كَذَٰلِكَ يُحْىِ ٱللَّهُ ٱلْمَوْتَىٰ وَيُرِيكُمْ ءَايَٰتِهِۦ لَعَلَّكُمْ تَعْقِلُونَ","translation":"We said: \"Apply this [principle] to some of those [cases of unresolved murder]: in this way God saves lives from death and shows you His will, so that you might [learn to] use your reason.\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/80.mp3","surahId":2,"words":[{"id":61038,"position":1,"arabic":"فَقُلْنَا","translation":"আমরা তখন বলেছিলাম","audioUrl":"wbw/002_073_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61039,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱضْرِبُوهُ","translation":"''তাকে তোমরা আঘাত কর","audioUrl":"wbw/002_073_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61040,"position":3,"arabic":"بِبَعْضِهَا ۚ","translation":"তার কিছু অংশ দিয়ে (এবং সে বেঁচে উঠল)''","audioUrl":"wbw/002_073_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61042,"position":4,"arabic":"كَذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এভাবে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_073_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61043,"position":5,"arabic":"يُحْىِ","translation":"জীবিত করেন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_073_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61044,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ্‌","audioUrl":"wbw/002_073_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61045,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْمَوْتَىٰ","translation":"মৃতকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_073_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61046,"position":8,"arabic":"وَيُرِيكُمْ","translation":"এবং তোমাদের দেখান","audioUrl":"wbw/002_073_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61047,"position":9,"arabic":"ءَايَـٰتِهِۦ","translation":"তাঁর নিদর্শনগুলোকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_073_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61048,"position":10,"arabic":"لَعَلَّكُمْ","translation":"তোমরা যাতে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_073_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61049,"position":11,"arabic":"تَعْقِلُونَ","translation":"বুঝতে পার","audioUrl":"wbw/002_073_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61050,"position":12,"arabic":"٧٣","translation":"(৭৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":74,"arabic":"ثُمَّ قَسَتْ قُلُوبُكُم مِّنۢ بَعْدِ ذَٰلِكَ فَهِىَ كَٱلْحِجَارَةِ أَوْ أَشَدُّ قَسْوَةًۭ ۚ وَإِنَّ مِنَ ٱلْحِجَارَةِ لَمَا يَتَفَجَّرُ مِنْهُ ٱلْأَنْهَٰرُ ۚ وَإِنَّ مِنْهَا لَمَا يَشَّقَّقُ فَيَخْرُجُ مِنْهُ ٱلْمَآءُ ۚ وَإِنَّ مِنْهَا لَمَا يَهْبِطُ مِنْ خَشْيَةِ ٱللَّهِ ۗ وَمَا ٱللَّهُ بِغَٰفِلٍ عَمَّا تَعْمَلُونَ","translation":"And yet, after all this, your hearts hardened and became like rocks, or even harder: for, behold, there are rocks from which streams gush forth; and, behold, there are some from which, when they are cleft, water issues; and, behold, there are some that fall down for awe of God And God is not unmindful of what you do!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/81.mp3","surahId":2,"words":[{"id":61517,"position":1,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"পরে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_074_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61518,"position":2,"arabic":"قَسَتْ","translation":"কঠিন হয়ে গেল","audioUrl":"wbw/002_074_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61519,"position":3,"arabic":"قُلُوبُكُم","translation":"তোমাদের অন্তরগুলো","audioUrl":"wbw/002_074_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61520,"position":4,"arabic":"مِّنۢ","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_074_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61521,"position":5,"arabic":"بَعْدِ","translation":"পরে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_074_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61522,"position":6,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এর","audioUrl":"wbw/002_074_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61523,"position":7,"arabic":"فَهِىَ","transla